<?php die('Unauthorized access.'); ?>a:39:{s:2:"id";s:1:"2";s:4:"type";s:8:"document";s:11:"contentType";s:9:"text/html";s:9:"pagetitle";s:8:"Visitors";s:9:"longtitle";s:48:"As A New Visitor, What Can I Expect at Mt. Zion?";s:11:"description";s:15:"A Loving Church";s:5:"alias";s:7:"visitor";s:15:"link_attributes";s:0:"";s:9:"published";s:1:"1";s:8:"pub_date";s:1:"0";s:10:"unpub_date";s:1:"0";s:6:"parent";s:1:"1";s:8:"isfolder";s:1:"0";s:9:"introtext";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:2879:"<h3>A Loving Church </h3><p>At Mt Zion we are excited that you are considering visiting us. We encourage you to come out and experience a Bible-based and relevant message, inspirational music, friendly people, and a loving environment. We desire to answer any questions you may have as a first time guest with us:</p><ul>	<li><a href="http://family.mtzioncary.org/home/top-navigation/directions.html" title="location"><em>Where are you located</em></a></li>					<li><a href="#dress" title="Dress Code Anchor">Do you have a dress code</a></li>					<li><em><a href="http://family.mtzioncary.org/home/ministries/christian_education/childrens_ministry.html" title="children">What is available for my children</a></em></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The following describes what we hope you will experience at our church: </p><h3>The Word </h3><p>The Word of God at Mt Zion is taught with clarity, conciseness, and creativity. The Gospel is preached to bring people to salvation in Jesus Christ. The Word of God is equipping us to let the light of Jesus shine through us to the world. We are to be a light to the world and a city on a hill that cannot be hidden. </p><h3>The Music </h3><p><em><a href="http://family.mtzioncary.org/home/ministries/worship/music_ministry.html">The music</a></em> is an integral part of our Christian worship experience. Our music ministry encompasses children from age 5 to adult whom use their worship through music to lead our congregation to new heights. At Mt Zion the music atmosphere is one of praise, worship, adoration, and celebration as we lift up Jesus Christ. The music and technology used at Mt Zion to enhance our worship is among the top 5% of churches across NC. </p><h3>Facilities </h3><p>Our facilities include a sanctuary large enough to accomodate members, guest, and visitors with room to spare. We have a multi-purpose facility with many rooms used for classrooms, fellowship, and ministry planning. We have a commercially equipped kitchen, and <em><a href="http://family.mtzioncary.org/home/ministries/service/it_media_ministry.html" title="itandmedia">IT/Media</a></em> room with quality video, audio, and lighting systems. We have a stage utilized for music and fine arts programs. Our location also host&nbsp;<!-- <a href="http://family.mtzioncary.org/assets/files/multimedia/general/MZ_Wedding_Brochure.pdf">-->weddings&nbsp;<!--</a> -->for both members and non-members. We have conveniently  located pastoral and administrative offices, a nursery, and conference rooms. Basically we are blessed with facilities that can meet spiritual and physical needs. </p><h3><a name="dress" title="dress"></a>Dress Code </h3><p>There is no dress code for our guests. Please come as you are. All are welcome. </p><script type="text/javascript">var woopra_id = '1878882349';</script><script src="http://static.woopra.com/js/woopra.js"></script>";s:8:"richtext";s:1:"1";s:8:"template";s:1:"5";s:9:"menuindex";s:1:"0";s:10:"searchable";s:1:"1";s:9:"cacheable";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdby";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdon";s:10:"1197590096";s:8:"editedby";s:1:"1";s:8:"editedon";s:10:"1249433677";s:7:"deleted";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedon";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedby";s:1:"0";s:11:"publishedon";s:10:"1197596400";s:11:"publishedby";s:1:"1";s:9:"menutitle";s:30:"What Can I Expect at Mt. Zion?";s:7:"donthit";s:1:"0";s:11:"haskeywords";s:1:"0";s:11:"hasmetatags";s:1:"0";s:10:"privateweb";s:1:"0";s:10:"privatemgr";s:1:"0";s:13:"content_dispo";s:1:"0";s:8:"hidemenu";s:1:"0";s:12:"MtZionFamily";a:5:{i:0;s:12